     <body>
     <div type="encomium">
   <pb facs="8"/>
   <head>To his old friend M<seg rend="sup">r</seg> FULLER.</head>
   <lg>
      <l>
         <hi>I</hi> Love no warres,</l>
      <l>I love no jarres,</l>
      <l>Nor strifes fire:</l>
      <l>May discords cease;</l>
      <l>Let's live in peace;</l>
      <l>This I desire.</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>If it must be</l>
      <l>Warre we must see</l>
      <l>(So Fates conspire)</l>
      <l>May we not feel</l>
      <l>The force of steel;</l>
      <l>This I desire:</l>
   </lg>
   <lg>
      <l>But in thy book</l>
      <l>When I do look</l>
      <l>And it admire;</l>
      <l>Let <hi>Warre</hi> be there,</l>
      <l>But Peace elswhere;</l>
      <l>This I desire.</l>
   </lg>
   <closer>
      <signed>Tho. Jackson.</signed>
   </closer>
</div>
